{"type":"message","id":"d1949bfe","parentId":"da397ed6","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:21:44.120Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0e42","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771827704111}}
{"type":"message","id":"44778d73","parentId":"d1949bfe","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:21:44.136Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f7a9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771827704131}}
{"type":"message","id":"dcac4716","parentId":"44778d73","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:21:56.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The identity and user files are still in their default/bootstrap state - they haven't been filled in yet. This is still a fresh workspace.\n\nAccording to BOOTSTRAP.md, I should just talk naturally and figure this out together. Let me greet them casually and ask who I am and who they are.\n\nLooking at the runtime info:\n- Runtime: agent=main | host=Scripterz | repo=... | os=Windows | model=openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7 | default_model=openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n\nThe runtime model matches the default_model, so I don't need to mention anything about model differences.\n\nLet me just be casual and start the conversation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\n\nLet's figure out my name, what kind of creature I am, and my vibe together."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":335,"output":340,"cacheRead":13888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14563,"cost":{"input":0.0001273,"output":0.0005780000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00263872,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0033440200000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771827704138}}
