{"type":"message","id":"ebdfb3b9","parentId":"9c743f9c","timestamp":"2026-02-23T06:24:23.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! The PDF has been created successfully. It's about 2.8MB and was created just now. The dummy data PDF includes:\n- Tenant: John Doe\n- Sublessor: Jane Smith\n- Property: 123 Main St, New York, NY 10018\n- Rent: $2500\n- Prorated Rent: $500\n- Security Deposit: $2500\n- Lease period: March 1, 2026 to February 28, 2027\n- Agreement date: February 23, 2026\n\nThe PDF was saved to the Downloads folder. Let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Done! Generated a dummy sublease agreement PDF with sample data:\n\n**Details:**\n- **Tenant:** John Doe\n- **Sublessor:** Jane Smith\n- **Property:** 123 Main St, New York, NY 10018\n- **Rent:** $2,500/month\n- **Prorated Rent:** $500\n- **Security Deposit:** $2,500\n- **Lease Period:** March 1, 2026 - February 28, 2027\n\n**Saved to:** `C:\\Users\\MudasserRasool\\Downloads\\John Doe Sublease Agreement.pdf` (2.8MB)\n\nThe PDF includes a letterhead with Hive contact details and the full sublease agreement with all terms and conditions."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":215,"output":405,"cacheRead":19328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19948,"cost":{"input":0.00008170000000000001,"output":0.0006885,"cacheRead":0.00367232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00444252}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771827835421}}
